            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucio</ex></expan> Peda</supplied>nio <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> Atili<lb break="no" n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">ano a</supplied>edili cui <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr><supplied reason="lost">Pe</supplied>d</abbr><ex>anius</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Paternus pater <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">st</supplied>at<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">uam aeneam</supplied> <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">po</supplied>nendam destina<lb break="no" n="6"/><supplied reason="lost">ve</supplied>rat heredes Iul<supplied reason="lost">ius</supplied> <lb n="7"/><supplied reason="lost">Eu</supplied>tychianus Peda<supplied reason="lost">nii</supplied> <lb n="8"/><supplied reason="lost">I</supplied>renicus et Irene <lb n="9"/><supplied reason="lost">P</supplied>omponia Philete <lb n="10"/><supplied reason="lost">u</supplied>xor voluntati <lb n="11"/><supplied reason="lost">ei</supplied>us satisfecerunt <lb n="12"/><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ocus</ex></expan></supplied> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>atus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecreto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecurionum</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Mittelteil einer Statuenbasis. Inschriftenfeld mittlerweile stark beschädigt, nur noch einzelne Buchstaben ab der fünften Zeile zu erkennen. Rekonstruktion daher durch Nutzung der handschriftlichen Überlieferung. Z. 4: statt aeneam? auch eius? denkbar.</p>
            </div>
